data.title: Christianna Elliott
data.content: I get excited about immersive art and projects, which makes the news of @statelibrarynsw’s latest project a thrill! Mine reflects the desire for a great selfie and fake smile, the perfection sought through make up, and the status of metallics in the modern age. Tag your NSW self with the hashtag #newselfwales to be included in their project, opening in October. #statelibrary #statelibraryofnsw #portrait #NSW #letmetakeaselfie #stateoforiginnightnoless
